The paper discusses the performance of energy detection for spectrum sensing over fading channels in cognitive radio networks, which involves topics related to information theory (cs.IT), network infrastructure (cs.NI), cognitive radio (cs.CR), system and control (cs.SY), and communication (cs.COM). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
